CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 18, 1960, pg. 5 reads: "11. Vera Washington and sales representative Larry Stahl dispensed gallons of refreshing Meadow Gold Dairies orange juice from the Meadow Gold Booth."
TitMainTitle: Vera Washington and Larry Stahl standing in Meadow Gold Milk booth in Syria Mosque for the 1960 Courier-WAMO Home-A-Rama
